    "body": "So if I'm interpreting this correctly, `MatlabMagics` should just set `initialized = False`, and move the following as arguments to the line magic:\n\n``` python\n                 matlab='matlab',\n                 maxtime=60,\n                 pyconverter=np.asarray,\n                 cache_display_data=False):\n```\n\nIf `initialized` is False or `matlab` changes, then we start a session.\n"
